uous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://tekton.dev/","primary_repository_url":"https://github.com/tektoncd/pipeline"},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--terramate","name":"Terramate","logo":"logos/dda6c0e5578317868f82050ce5693aeb00e2e58c4396baaadac73da1c68677b6.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://www.terramate.io/","description":"Terramate is an Infrastructure as Code (IaC) Management Platform combining Infrastructure Delivery, Drift Management, Observability, and Collaboration in a single platform that developers are excited about. We focus on providing the best developer experience by combining workflows, best practices, and more so that developers can move beyond infrastructure and focus on developing applications.","member_subcategory":"Silver","primary_repository_url":"https://github.com/terramate-io/terramate"},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--testkube","name":"Testkube","logo":"logos/43d6bc92e123e2fed024b7798b6e6beb689c811847afa91fc57700837f0d97e1.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://testkube.io","description":"Testkube provides a Kubernetes-native framework for test definition, execution and results. It decouples test artifacts and execution from CI/CD tooling and makes testing part of your cluster's state. Testkube is built and maintained by Kubeshop.","member_subcategory":"Silver","primary_repository_url":"https://github.com/kubeshop/testkube"},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--travis-ci","name":"Travis CI","logo":"logos/bcc39e623cb15087517ea8596e4ef068b33e489b9a66741fa6223b4e62dec7ff.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://travis-ci.com/","primary_repository_url":"https://github.com/travis-ci/travis-web"},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--werf","name":"werf","logo":"logos/c2af80744abaa2cfedfcf10e3b0b84db36099f12310e900f50b4c436165b1658.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://werf.io/","description":"werf is a solution for implementing efficient and consistent software delivery to Kubernetes. It covers the entire CI/CD lifecycle and all related artifacts, glues commonly used tools (Git, Docker/Buildah, Helm, K8s) and facilitates best practices.","maturity":"sandbox","primary_repository_url":"https://github.com/werf/werf","tag":["app-delivery"]},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--woodpecker-ci","name":"Woodpecker CI","logo":"logos/d38ac3329368e41e8286ac247ec095b27169c0b1f8fe524929eea7764faef1d3.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://woodpecker-ci.org","primary_repository_url":"https://github.com/woodpecker-ci/woodpecker"},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--xl-deploy","name":"XL Deploy","logo":"logos/099070ffd7a312187e3806157bbfa65bc73fb2e93aef8f3a42ec6eae1ec582c0.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://digital.ai/deploy/deployment-automation"},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--kube-burner","name":"Kube-burner","logo":"logos/994a5fdc1fbd3f3723646d0dcdd73a29e3e6f4719c763a67b18106231f26faa1.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://kube-burner.github.io/kube-burner/","maturity":"sandbox","member_subcategory":"Platinum","primary_repository_url":"https://github.com/kube-burner/kube-burner","tag":["app-delivery"]},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--omnistrate-member","name":"Omnistrate (member)","logo":"logos/4953ac94e818961d0a2a5b233f4f1d35a6e5ae0ed156be245cb4e7814e14ef84.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://omnistrate.ai","description":"Omnistrate is a CoPilot for platform teams — helping them build software and agent platforms and turn cloud-native projects into production-ready  platforms without years of custom glue code. Instead of stitching together CI/CD, runtimes, infra-as-code, Day-2 operations, integrations, and  billing from scratch for every customer — and making it all work across clouds, regions, accounts, and deployment configurations — Omnistrate  provides ready-to-use modules that integrate directly with the CNCF ecosystem: Kubernetes, Argo, Flux, Helm, Operators, Kustomize, Terraform,  Prometheus, and more. By building on top of CNCF projects rather than reinventing them, Omnistrate enables modern software companies to deliver  applications in any model — OnPrem, BYOC, PaaS, SaaS, or Agent-aaS — in days, not years."},{"category":"App Definition and Development","id":"app-definition-and-development--continuous-integration-delivery--zuul","name":"Zuul","logo":"logos/8238ff6c44bf1123614a436a3dabfcc19df2e6aa28f196f6036e402f70899b2f.svg","subcategory":"Continuous Integration & Delivery","website":"https://zuul-ci.org","description":"Zuul is a system that drives continuous integration, delivery, and deployment with a focus on project gating and interrelated projects.","primary_repository_url":"https://opendev.org/zuul/zuul"}]}